org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_Foundations.GRM

Interface SchedulableResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GaCommChannel, SwSchedulableResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GaCommChannelImpl, SchedulableResourceImpl, SwSchedulableResourceImpl

    public interface SchedulableResource
extends Resource
    A representation of the model object 'Schedulable Resource'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Sched Params
    • Dependent Scheduler
    • Host

    See Also:
    GRMPackage.getSchedulableResource()
